    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Starting when you choose this path at 3rd level, spectral warriors appear when you enter your rage. While you are raging, the first creature you hit with an attack on your turn becomes the target of the warriors, which hinder its attacks. Until the start of your next turn, that target has disadvantage on any attack roll that is not against you, and when the target deals damage to a creature other than you, that creature has resistance to the damage dealt by to them. The effect on the target ends early if your rage ends.</p>",
